<br />
But im not really sure of what configuration i want/need.<br />
<br />
I'll use it to work but i want to be able to play games on it too (like WoW) so when i come back i can use it when i play with friends.<br />
<br />
As i will need to move it around i was thinking of a 15.4" screen size. 1 or 2gb ram, approx 100 gb, intel duo core 2 at 1,88 ghz  should be the base.<br />
<br />
My main problem is in the choice of the graphic card, and i don't know if some  brand (can i say "brand" in english speaking of laptop?) like Dell, Hp, Acer...are good or not.<br />
<br />
I need your input ! :typeing: <br />
<br />
Thanks for any advice</div>
