<br />
If you don't mind the weight you can pick up a 1705 notebook with 17 inch widescreen and nvidia graphics card...it's about a pound and half heavier i belive....a lot depends on how much you want to spend too....hope this info helps if you need more let me know and i'll go into detail....</div>
